  <span id="freeText8012672695384519413" style="display:none">A very good book on the concept of space and what it's made of explained in a clear and simple yet comprehensive manner by a brilliant physicist. You also learn a little about string theory and quantum loop theory and how they strive to come up with a theory of quantum gravity. </span>
