<li class='cover' id='bookCover_2099'>
<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/2099.Stephen_Hawking_s_Universe"><img alt="Stephen Hawking&#39;s Universe: The Cosmos Explained" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1436062602l/2099._SX98_.jpg" />
